The testcases are provided in the folder testcases.
To run any testcase just bring it to the current folder containing makefile and just 
rename it to input.txt and open terminal here and just type make.

The program display total number of instructions
CPI,IPC and total no of clock cycles


We have a memory array of 1500 size only so use carefully.
You can use the immediate operand in str and ldr instructions like #4 for going
to next address like for int the program will automatically divide it and use the appropriate memory
